            "body": "You have a trailing space in the `:normal` command. Remove the trailing space:\r\n```lua\r\nlocal c1 = vim.api.nvim_win_get_cursor(0) \r\nvim.cmd[[normal! ma]]\r\nlocal c2 = vim.api.nvim_win_get_cursor(0) \r\nprint(c1[2], c2[2])\r\n```",
